<H3> <TI>   Gunmen Hold Four Hostage in Durban House of Delegates </TI></H3>
<H4>   Two Men Involved </H4>
<F P=102> MB1002171194 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network in 
English 1600 GMT 10 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> MB1002171194 </F>
<F P=104>  Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Four people are being held hostage at the House of 
Delegates building in Durban. Police spokesman Captain Henry 
Budram said it was believed that two armed men were holding 
staff members at Truro House hostage. The gunmen's demands are 
not yet known. 

</TEXT>

