<H3> <TI>   Gunmen Kill Azapo Official in Soweto 13 Feb </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  MB1402080894 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network in 
English 0500 GMT 14 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> MB1402080894 </F>
<F P=104>  Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] A leading member of the Azanian People's Liberation 
Army [Azapo], Mr. Letsatsi Mosala, has been shot dead by unknown 
gunmen in Soweto, near Johannesburg. Mr. Mosala, a member of 
Azapo's strategy committee and a former national organizer for 
the organization, was shot at point blank range while driving 
through the Rockville area of Soweto last night. The gunmen 
escaped in his car. 

</TEXT>

