<ABS>  FOUO </ABS>
<DATE1>   1 March 1994 </DATE1>
<F P=100> NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA </F>
<F P=101> REGIONAL AFFAIRS </F>
<H3> <TI>   Update on Jordanian Diplomat's Killing in Beirut </TI></H3>
<H4>   Palestinians Confess </H4>
<F P=102> NC1602172594 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1630 GMT 16 Feb 
94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1602172594 </F>
