<H3> <TI>   Islamic Group Attacks Bus Carrying Romanians </TI></H3>
<H4>   No Casualties in Bus Attack </H4>
<F P=102> NC1402134494 Cairo MENA in Arabic 1300 GMT 14 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC1402134494 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Asyut, 14 Feb (MENA)--Three unknown gunmen fired at 
a minibus in the al-Sadat area in the city of Asyut, Upper 
Egypt. There were no casualties. 
  According to initial reports, the minibus was carrying 10 
passengers, two Egyptians and eight Romanian experts working at 
a cement factory in the region. 
  The culprits fired at the minibus using handguns; they 
caused 
damage to the right side of the minibus. 
  Officials of the Asyut Security Directorate, Public 
Security, 
and Criminal Investigations rushed to the scene. The 
prosecution office was informed to begin investigations. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

<DOC>
<DOCNO> FBIS3-22965 </DOCNO>
