Assam] militants shot dead the general manager of a tea company 
early this morning at (Talab) Tea Estate of Tinsukhia District 
in upper Assam. Police sources at Guwahati said the miscreants 
stole his vehicle, which was recovered later from a nearby 
village. A vigorous manhunt is on to nab the culprits. 

