<F P=102>  NC1402202294 (Clandestine) Voice of Independent Kurdistan in 
Turkish 1300 GMT 13 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1402202294 </F>
<F P=104>  (Clandestine) Voice of Independent Kurdistan </F>


