<H3> <TI>   Dev-Sol Bombing Team Captured in Black Sea City </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA1702161794 Ankara ANATOLIA in English 1515 GMT 17 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> TA1702161794 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara ANATOLIA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Samsun, Feb 17 (AA) -- Security teams caught five 
members of the THKP-C [Turkish People's Liberation Party Front] 
Dev-Sol [Revolutionary Left] terror organization in this Black 
Sea city on Wednesday. 
  AA learned that acting on a tip-off, anti-terror teams 
raided 
a house in the city, capturing Celal Ozkul, the Black Sea region 
official of the organization and four others. 
  A revolver, shells, a copy machine, material used in 
explosives, and organizational documents were found in the house. 
  Officials of the security directorate said that the five 
people caught were a bombing team and were preparing for terror 
actions in the Black Sea region. 

