country. The king did not disclose the name of that country. 
An official Jordanian source, however, told our radio that the 
Arab country is Libya and that the group, which carried out the 
operation, is Fatah-the Revolutionary Council led by Abu-Nidal 
[Sabri al-Banna]. [passage omitted] 

