<H3> <TI>   Three Police Hijack Airliner, Seek Asylum in Spain </TI></H3>
<H4>   Hijackers Were Dismissed From Police </H4>
<F P=102> LD0103233994 Algiers Radio Algiers Network in Arabic 2300 
GMT 1 Mar 94 </F>

