<H3> <TI>   `Militants' Shoot Policeman in Idfu; Police Kill Several Suspects </TI></H3>
<H4>   Militants Tracked Down in Idfu </H4>
<F P=102> NC2802090094 Paris AFP in English 0851 GMT 28 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC2802090094 </F>
<F P=104>  Paris AFP </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, Feb 28 (AFP)--Egyptian police shot dead four 
suspected Muslim militants overnight in the southern city of 
Aswan, the security services said Monday. 
  The militants were tracked down after they killed a 
policeman 
late Sunday in Idfu, 100 kilometres (60 miles) north of Aswan. 

</TEXT>

