<H3> <TI>   `Militants' Shoot Policeman in Idfu; Police Kill Several Suspects </TI></H3>
<H4>   MENA Reports Two More Dead </H4>
<F P=102> NC2802144294 Cairo MENA in Arabic 1300 GMT 28 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC2802144294 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Aswan, 28 Feb (MENA)--Security forces killed five 
terrorists today following a chase through farm areas in Aswan. 
  The incident took place during sweeps that began last night 
in Aswan. Security organs killed three wanted terrorists last 
night after they attacked a policeman. 
  According to security sources, the dead men were dangerous 
terrorists wanted by the police in connection with several 
crimes. 

</TEXT>

