<H3> <TI>   More Bank Bombings </TI></H3>
<H4>   Leader of Organization Caught </H4>
<F P=102> NC0303073094 Cairo AL-AKHBAR in Arabic 28 Feb 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> NC0303073094 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo AL-AKHBAR </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Report by Muhammad Salah al-Zahhar] </F>
  [Text] The security agencies have gathered important 
information in their search for the organization responsible for 
detonating explosive devices in front of banks. The security 
agencies have identified a large number of persons suspected of 
having carried out these operations and have arrested a number 
of them. 
  The leader of this organization has been identified and 
arrested in one of the governorates. He was found in possession 
of a large quantity of explosives and ammunition and a new plan 
for detonating devices with a timer that was used for the first 
time in the devices that exploded in al-Jizah last week. The 
arrested defendants gave detailed confession about their 
terrorist plan, which sought to create panic and instability in 
Egypt. 

</TEXT>

