<H3> <TI>   More Bank Bombings </TI></H3>
<H4>   Bank Misr Branch in Abu Tij Attacked </H4>
<F P=102> NC0203074594 Cairo MENA in Arabic 0725 GMT 2 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0203074594 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] Cairo, 2 Mar (MENA)--A responsible security 
source at the Interior Ministry said today that at approximately 
2015 last night, three unidentified persons opened fire on and 
threw an explosive device at the Bank Misr branch in the city of 
Abu Tij, Asyut Governorate. The security source added that the 
bank's guard returned fire, forcing the gunmen to flee. The 
source pointed out that there were no casualties. Property 
damage was confined to the bank's windows, which were smashed. 
[passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

