<H3> <TI>   Unidentified Gunmen Kill Policeman in Asyut </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC0303124794 Cairo MENA in Arabic 1212 GMT 3 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0303124794 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Asyut, 3 Mar (MENA)--Police Warrant Officer Muhammad 
'Atif of al-Badari Police Station in Asyut was shot and killed 
by unknown assailants today. 
  Two citizens, Hilmi Muhammad Hasan, 45, and his son Radwan, 
20, who were walking with the policeman, were injured by the 
gunfire. 
  The security forces cordoned off the area and mounted a 
search for the culprits. The Prosecutor's Office began an 
investigation. 

</TEXT>

