<H3> <TI>   Update on, Reactions to Hebron Mosque Massacre </TI></H3>
<H4>   Police To Seize `Extremists' Automatic Weapons </H4>
<F P=102> TA2802165494 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1600 GMT 28 
Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA2802165494 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Hebrew </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The police minister has ordered the confiscation of 
the automatic weapons of extremist settlers in Judaea and 
Samaria, but let them keep their personal weapons, such as guns. 
He also ordered the police commissioner to release all the 
Israeli Arabs who were arrested during demonstrations in the 
last few days if they are not suspected of having hit policemen 
or damaged property. 

</TEXT>

