<H3> <TI>   Bomb in Zuq Musbih Church Kills 10, Injures 40 </TI></H3>
<H4>   `Big Explosion' In Church, Casualties </H4>
<F P=102> NC2702080194 (Clandestine) Radio Free Lebanon in Arabic 0747 
GMT 27 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC2702080194 </F>
<F P=104>  (Clandestine) Radio Free Lebanon </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [See SELECTED VIDEO REPORTS in the front of this Terrorism </F>
Report for TV coverage of this incident] 
  [Excerpt] A horrendous crime with the proportions of a 
massacre was committed in the Church of Sayyidat al-Najat in 
Wata Zuq Mich'il a short while ago. A big explosion occurred in 
the church while worshippers were taking part in a mass. 
Initial information indicates that a large number of people 
were killed or injured. Casualties are being taken to the 
hospitals in the area, particularly the Sayyidat Lubnan 
Hospital, which is crowded with casualties. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

