Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpts] Investigative Police on 9 March at noon finally 
arrested Rosa Ester Vargas, the original mujer metralleta 
[submachine gun woman], who is regarded as the most dangerous 
subversive in the Lautaro group. She was arrested in the 
country's southern section with two other people. She was 
transferred today to a Civilian Police post under strict 
security measures. [passage omitted] 
  Vargas participated mainly in attacks on banks. Police 
reported her arrest to Special Judge (Arnoldo Ereise), who 
investigates the subversive group's actions. She will be placed 
at his disposal in 10 days. 

