  [Text] In another development, security services announced 
today that three members of armed groups were killed during the 
last 24 hours in Constantine, Boumerdes, and Ain Defla. 
  Security services also said that it arrested six other 
members of the armed groups during the same period in Bouira, 
Tipaza and Boumerdes. In the capital, security services have 
