<H3> <TI>   Sayah Attia New Armed Islamic Group Chief </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  BR0903113794 Paris LE FIGARO in French 9 Mar 94 p 4 </F>
<F P=103> BR0903113794 </F>
<F P=104>  Paris LE FIGARO </F>


<TEXT>
