<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Asyut, 7 Mar (MENA)--An explosive device was 
detonated in front of the Badr Hotel near Asyut's railroad 
station. The loud explosion, which occurred shortly after the 
fast breaking evening meal today, rocked the area but caused no 
casualties or property damage. 
  The security forces and explosives experts defused another 
time bomb in the Banks Square in city. The security forces 
cordoned off the area and mounted a search for possible suspects. 

