<H3> <TI>   `Fugitive Terrorist' Arrested in Western Alexandria </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC0903161194 Cairo MENA in Arabic 1420 GMT 9 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0903161194 </F>
