<H3> <TI>   Bomb Placed in Front of French Cultural Center </TI></H3>
<H4>   Device Defused </H4>
<F P=102> NC0903084694 Beirut Voice of Lebanon in Arabic 0815 GMT 9 
Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC0903084694 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Voice of Lebanon </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] A military source has stated that at about 0900 
today, according to a tip by a citizen, Lebanese Army units 
found an explosive charge containing six kg of explosives packed 
like a present and placed near the French Cultural Center in the 
township of Ghadir in Kasrawan. The units cordoned off the area 
and a military expert defused the charge in coordination with 
the Internal Security Forces. It should be recalled that 
certain people earlier protested the decision to close down the 
French Cultural Center and move it to another area. 

</TEXT>

