<H3> <TI>   PFLP-GC Gives Militiaman to Hizballah in `Prisoner' Exchange </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  JN1003081594 Paris Radio Monte Carlo in Arabic 0600 GMT 10 
Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN1003081594 </F>
<F P=104>  Paris Radio Monte Carlo </F>


