Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] A statement by the Ahmad Jibril's Popular Front for 
the Liberation of Palestine-General Command [PFLP-GC] says that 
the PFLP-GC captured a pro-Israeli militiaman in southern 
Lebanon and turned him over to Hizballah in exchange for women 
and girls detained in Israeli and militia prisons. The 
